quit;
```

In this code, `ranuni(0,1,N)` generates N random numbers from a uniform distribution on the interval (0, 1). We multiply the first set of random numbers by 1 and divide the second set by 1, thus maintaining the desired ratio of two random numbers. The result is then printed out.

